If you use the OSS sound system you may need to install audio/alsa-plugins
to enable sound output for your hardware. Then edit ~/.asoundrc to contain
(for NetBSD):

pcm.!default {
	type oss
	device /dev/audio
}

ctl.!default {
	type oss
	device /dev/mixer
}

===========================================================================
